这不是在VR Live中实时拍摄的图像，而不是MV屏幕吗？</span></strong></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.9kzavnhqlrm7-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.9kzavnhqlrm7-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.9kzavnhqlrm7-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.9kzavnhqlrm7-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.9kzavnhqlrm7-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.9kzavnhqlrm7-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.9kzavnhqlrm7-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>从那里，再次发生空间转移！在第五首歌<strong>“ Shonen Manga”</strong>中，Ciel -Chan在舞台上脱颖而出，就像由许多块制成的巨大舞台。<strong>聚光灯很美！</strong></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.v68e2h4d9egt-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.v68e2h4d9egt-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.v68e2h4d9egt-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.v68e2h4d9egt-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.v68e2h4d9egt-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.v68e2h4d9egt-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix