的形状，对歌曲的响应散发出来，以及<strong>像Ciel的幻觉一样的光线</strong>出现并在舞台上自由飞行再次非常复杂的生产。</p><p><strong>太免费...！ ！这是“幻想戏剧” ...！</strong></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="57