4/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6xm4mvijvojf-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6xm4mvijvojf-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6xm4mvijvojf-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6xm4mvijvojf-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6xm4mvijvojf-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>第六首歌结束了，最后是最后一首歌。 Ciel -chan回顾了插入水时间后2021年首次亮相的轨迹，说“我有点太坚固”（可爱...）。</p><p>我们将有一个热情的观看，并感谢您能够进行各种活动，并谈论我们在歌曲中提出的想法和活动的暂停。他在场地告诉粉丝，他真的很高兴见到，唱歌<strong>和爱，并与最后一首歌联系在一起，说：“我会以所有的感受和所有的感觉唱歌。”</strong></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.u1w11zrd0ltg-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.u1w11zrd0ltg-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.u1w11zrd0ltg-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.u1w11zrd0ltg-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.u1w11zrd0ltg-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.u1w11zrd0ltg-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.u1w11zrd0ltg-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zfz968u6yw5u-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zfz968u6yw5u-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zfz968u6yw5u-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zfz968u6yw5u-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zfz968u6yw5u-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zfz968u6yw5u-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zfz968u6yw5u-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>第七首歌是<strong>“您的希望，您的愿望”</strong> 。这是一个适合上一首歌的数字，对重要人物有着强烈的思考。</p><p><strong>白光像花瓣一样，与Ciel -Chan的短暂和透明的歌声聚集在一起，并在整个场地上飙升</strong>。我觉得Ciel -Chan的思想被放在许多温暖的灯光中，这些灯光在绘制轨迹时飞走了。<br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.sfgrzji4j8zw-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.sfgrzji4j8zw-576x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.sfgrzji4j8zw-576x1024.webp 576w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.sfgrzji4j8zw-169x300.webp 169w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.sfgrzji4j8zw-768x1365.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.sfgrzji4j8zw-864x1536.webp 864w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.sfgrzji4j8zw-jpg.webp 900w" width="576" height="1024" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.3cltvs7bfr58-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.mogur